title: Spacious 2bed 2bath POSSIBLY COMING SOON! Northern Pines Apartments
posting_body: ['Spacious 2 bedroom two bath apartment homes.', ' COMING SOON!!!', 'Possibly As early as October2022', 'Northern Pines Apartment Homes.', 'Conveniently located at 774 Northern Ave.', 'Clarkston, GA 30021', 'Our contact information is:', 'show contact info', 'Northern Pines Apartments has a great Location!', 'Inside out lovely community we offer updated flooring, newly resurfaced tubs and countertops*, new window Blinds, separate laundry room area, 24 Hour Emergency Maintenance, our community is cable ready, online rental payments available and yes, we are pet friendly.', 'Located right off of I-285 Church Street Exit.', 'And just minutes from Northlake Mall, Restaurants, Banking, Stone Mountain Park and lots of shopping.', 'A few of our community amenities are we have  private patios and balconies included in each two bedroom  homes and there is also a picnic and BBQ area for your grilling pleasure.', 'Prices start as low as $1,250 (includes water)', 'Our days of operation are Mon/Weds/Friday of each week', 'Application fee is just $50.00 with a $150.00 reservation fee', 'Equal Housing opportunity', 'Prices are subject to change']
